summary: SummaryDiscover L'Or√©al's powdery matte Infallible Matte Resistance Liquid Lipstick that lasts up to 16 hours. Get bold color payoff in one swipe that's transfer & smudge-resistant, for an all-day matte finish.
details: DetailsFeaturesTransfer and smudge resistant for an all-day longwear matte finishWith a lightweight feel, Infused with Hyaluronic AcidBold color payoff in one effortless swipe with precise applicatorAvailable in multiple irresistible shades, Find yours todayBenefitsInfused with Hyaluronic acidItem 2610779How To UseUsing the precise applicator, apply starting in the center of your upper lip. how_to_use: Using the precise applicator, apply starting in the center of your upper lip. Work from the center to outer edges of your lips and then glide across the entire bottom lip.Flammable until dry. Do not use near fire, flame or heat.

reviews.headline: Overhyped
reviews.comments: I had high hopes for this liquid lipstick due to the reviews, but I am just not impressed with it. I used a makeup wipe to clean up some areas I applied out of my lip line - it just smeared and made a huge mess & left a red stain around my lips. I wouldn't recommend this.

reviews.comments: Easily lasted me 16+ hours through drinking, eating, and kissing. Didn't transfer to cups or utensils or my boyfriend lol. Light, comfortable feeling on lips, not drying at all. The only thing I'd change is I'd make the applicator a little smaller and more precise as it will stain the skin for 16+ hours if not applied correctly, but that's nothing using a precision lip brush and concealer wouldn't solve.

media.caption: Bold and Long-Lasting   I recently tried the Infallible Matte Resistance Liquid Lipstick in Shade 204, The¬†bold color and matte finish immediately caught my eye.¬†The color is a beautiful blend that is suitable for various occasions. I appreciate how the matte finish adds a touch of elegance, making it suitable for both everyday wear and special events.   I must say, it left a lasting impression! What impressed me the most is the longevity of this particular shade. It held up remarkably well, maintaining its intensity even after several hours. The formula feels comfortable on the lips,   One thing to note is that the formula can be a bit drying, so it's essential to moisturize your lips beforehand. Despite this, the long-lasting matte !  I give 5 stars, even though it is a bit dry, but i used a lot more expensive lipsticks, my lips still feel right. For the price and what it performs I highly recommend it for those seeking a versatile and long-lasting liquid lipstick that combines style with comfortable and pocket friendly

faceoff_positive.comments:
Run & Get It,
 Beacausr You're Worth It!
You Will Not Be Disappointed! Im a sucker for products that actually delivers results as they say. L'Oreal - Infallible Matte Resistance Liquid Lipstick is soo creamy, powdery liquid lipstick. Application is a breeze. With the precision applicator and formulas perfect consistency, it glides effortlessly across lips surface. Leaving lips looking and feeling fabulous. It's super lightweight, plus its infused with hyaluronic acid which provides you lips all day hydration. It doesn't stop there. After applied and dried it stays in place no need to constantly reapplying plus it's transfer-resistant and smudge-resistant. It comes in a variety of different fun, flirty sofistacated colors! This is the color shade Road Tripping.
faceoff_positive.headline: Road Tripping Lips- Because You're Worth It!

faceoff_negative.comments: The lip stick goes on smooth and dries to a matte finish.  The color I received was breakfast in bed.  It is a nude shade, I wish the color was a little warmer/darker it kind of gives an ashy appearance.  It is definitely long lasting.  One thing I might suggest is priming the lips before application to minimize the cracked lip appearance.  Overall, not bad, I would just have to find the right shade for me.
faceoff_negative.headline: I would buy this again but in a different color
